Amphibious man from "The Shape of water". (@shapeofwatermovie) 
This is my last and most difficult creation. I started this project for an exam of the special effects school I just finished. As a special effects technician, Guillermo Del Toro ( @realgdt ) is my messiah and his creatures are my greatest source of inspiration. I haven't been as good as him but I'll try to improve!
Thanks to @actordougjones to make this character so perfect!
God bless @maggieevans666 and @mikehillart for their artistry!!! .
